OL,5, A former right-wing extremist has      
OL,6, described how he was radicalised as a  
OL,7, 15-year-old boy in the wake of the     
OL,8, Manchester Arena bombing.              
OL,10,FJohn said he wanted to speak out as a  
OL,11,Fway of warning other young people,     
OL,12,Fparticularly about the dangers posed   
OL,13,Fonline.                                
OL,15,F"It was unbelievably easy as a young   
OL,16,Fteenager to access propaganda and now  
OL,17,Fit's just as easy - maybe easier," John
OL,18,Ftold BBC North West Tonight.           
